 done in Israel, "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"you are to bring out to your city gates that man or woman who has done this evil thing and stone them to death. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 22:24","book":"Deu","chapter":22,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 22:24","book":"Deu","chapter":22,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The one condemned to die is to be executed on the testimony of two or three witnesses. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 19:15","book":"Deu","chapter":19,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:16","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 13:1","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 5:19","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":19,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:28","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":28,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" No one is to be executed on the testimony of a single witness. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 19:15","book":"Deu","chapter":19,"verse":15},{"label":"Mt 18:16","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":16},{"label":"2Co 13:1","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":1},{"label":"1Tm 5:19","book":"1Ti","chapter":5,"verse":19},{"label":"Heb 10:28","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The witnesses’ hands are to be the first in putting him to death, and after that, the hands of all the people. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 13:9","book":"Deu","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" You must purge the evil from you. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 13:5","book":"Deu","chapter":13,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 19:19","book":"Deu","chapter":19,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","labe