ger behave arrogantly."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“When you enter the land the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God is giving you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 26:1","book":"Deu","chapter":26,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" take possession of it, live in it, and say, ‘I will set a king over me like all the nations around me,’ "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 26:1","book":"Deu","chapter":26,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"you are to appoint over you the king the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" your God chooses. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Sm 8:4","book":"1Sa","chapter":8,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Appoint a king from your brothers. You are not to set a foreigner over you, or one who is not of your people. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 17:6","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 17:16","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 35:11","book":"Gen","chapter":35,"verse":11,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nm 24:17","book":"Num","chapter":24,"verse":17,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Sm 8:4","book":"1Sa","chapter":8,"verse":4},{"label":"Gn 17:6","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":6},{"label":"Gn 17:16","book":"Gen","chapter":17,"verse":16},{"label":"Gn 35:11","book":"Gen","chapter":35,"verse":11},{"label":"Nm 24:17","book":"Num","chapter":24,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"However, he must not acquire many horses for himself or send the people back to Egypt to acquire many horses, for the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" has told you, ‘You are never to go back that way again.’ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 10:28","book":"1Ki","chapter":10,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 10:28","book":"1Ki","chapter":10,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He must not acquire many wives for himself so that his heart won’t go astray. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 11:3","book":"1Ki","chapter":11,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" He must not acquire very large amounts of silver and gold for himself. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 10:21","book":"1Ki","chapter":10,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 11:3","book":"1Ki","chapter":11,"verse":3},{"label":"1Kg 10:21","book":"1Ki","chapter":10,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When he is seated on his royal throne, he is to write a copy of this instruction for himself on a scroll in the presence of the Levitical priests. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"It is to remain with him, and he is to read from it all the days of his life, so that he may learn to fear "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 14:23","book":"Deu","chapter":14,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" his God, to observe all the words of this instruction, and to do these statutes. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 14:23","book":"Deu","chapter":14,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:17:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then his heart will not be exalted above his countrymen, he will not turn from this command to the right or the left, and he and his sons will continue reigning many years "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit will lengthen days on his kingdom"},{"kind":"text","text":" in Israel."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit will lengthen days on his kingdom"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783099263947}